Use the Case Detail page to see and update detailed information about a case, work with related lists, view approval history, add team members, close or delete cases.

Required Editions: Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, Developer
User Permissions: View on cases, Edit on cases, Delete on cases

Note: Inline editing enabled in some organizations. 

To switch between feed and details page, use buttons.
Open printable display of case details by clicking Printable View.
